c: 12
v: 110
t: "Nabiyow koo dirabboyse maral mayso geytaamih fayxit maasassakin kok duma warrayte farmoytiitih mayso mamattok, diggah usun (farmoytit kinnuk) sinni marih iimaanak obbodduuy usun ken dirabboyseenim ismitti haanam fanah, too waqdi Ni catoo kee Ni qokol kaxxa gibda ken xabba hayte waqdi keenih yemeete, tokkel nanu ninnih fanna mara naggosna digaalak, Ni digaala umeyniitih yan marak magacsimta"